SerialInputStreamTest, TelnetInputStreamTest
public abstract class SystemInputStreamTest
extends TestSuite

This is an abstract superclass intended to test the stream behaviour implemented in SystemInputStream- itself an abstract superclass. The tests run by calling the abstract method constructStream(java.io.InputStream, java.io.PrintStream), which returns an instance of the class to be tested. The behaviour tested here is a semi-random collection of behaviours which have been broken in various releases of the TINI OS.
